def research(x, y):
  print("================================", x.to_frame().columns[0]," ", y.to_frame().columns[0], "=============================================================================================")
  conTab = pd.crosstab(x, y, margins=True)
  table_expected = stats.contingency.expected_freq(conTab)
  print("----------------- -----------------\n", conTab, "\n-----------------  -----------------\n", table_expected)
  ntab = conTab.to_numpy()
  minAmt = data.shape[0]
  for i in range (0, conTab.shape[0]):
    for j in range (0, conTab.shape[1]):
      if ntab[i][j] < minAmt:
        num = ntab[i][j]
  if (minAmt >=10):                 #  -
    chi2 = stats.chi2_contingency(conTab, correction=False)
    print("---------------------- -----------------------\n\n\tcriteria_value = ", chi2[0],"\n\tp-value = ", chi2[1], "\n\t   = ", chi2[2], "\n\n", chi2[3])
  elif (minAmt<10 and minAmt >=5):                 #   
    chi2 = stats.chi2_contingency(conTab, correction=True)
    print("---------- -   ----------\n\n\tcriteria_value = ", chi2[0],"\n\tp-value = ", chi2[1], "\n\t   = ", chi2[2], "\n\n", chi2[3])
  elif (minAmt <5):

    for i in range (o, conTab.shape[0]):
      for j in range (0, conTab.shape[1]):
        if ntab[i][j] < 5:
          count += 1
    if (len(x)== 2 and len(y)== 2 and (count > 0.2 * ntab.shape[0]*ntab.shape[1])):                 #   
      fish_test = stats.fisher_exact(conTab)
      print("----------------------  ----------------------\n\n criteria_value = ", fish_test[0], "\n p-value = ", fish_test)
    else:
      fisher_result = stats_r.fisher_test(ntab, simulate_p_value = False)
      print("---------------------- -----------------------\n\n criteria_value = ", fisher_result[0], "\n p-value = ", fisher_result)

In [15]:
def income_label(value, left, right):
  return {
    value < left:  '',
    left <= value < right:  '',
    right <= value: ''
  }[True]
  
data["Income"] = data["Income"].apply(
    lambda x: income_label(x, data["Income"].quantile(0.3), data["Income"].quantile(0.7))
)
